messages.text: Hey.
Is this Tracy?
Yeah, what’s up?
Who’s this?
It’s Justin haha.
The guy from Mike’s Halloween party.
The one who you made out with…
In Mike’s bedroom haha?
Hahaha oh yes, I remember.
Last night is slowly starting to come back to me now.
This hangover is clouding my memory just a bit haha.
That’s good to hear haha.
I just wanted to follow up on last night though.
See how you’re doing…
And possibly…
See if you’re up to talking about what happened?
Wow, I forgot how forward you are.
But then again, considering the hickey on my neck…
Maybe I shouldn’t have haha ;)
Yeah, actually…
That’s one of the things I wanted to talk to you about.
Do you notice anything weird about that hickey I left you on your neck?
Well, now that you mention it…
I think you left a couple of marks there too.
Seems like we were a little bit rough last night haha.
Yeah, that’s what I was afraid of.
How are you feeling right now?
Uh, I’m fine besides, you know, being hungover and all that.
Why? Did you think you got me sick or something?
Well, not exactly but sort of, maybe? I don’t know.
You wouldn’t believe me if I told you.
Dude, try me haha.
All right, well, shit, I’ll just say it then.
I’m a vampire.
And I think I may have turned you into one.
Tracy, you there?
I’m here, I’m here.
I’ve just been laughing for like a minute straight haha.
I bet. I knew you wouldn’t believe me.
It sounds so fucking stupid, doesn’t it?
Yeah, just a tiny bit.
No offense.
If you gave me mono or something, you don’t have to lie to me.
I know I sound insane but I’m not lying.
I didn’t give you mono either.
So I’m seriously supposed to believe that you’re a vampire.
And you may have turned me into a vampire when you gave me a hickey?
Yeah, I know. It sounds really, really dumb.
Well, I mean I can’t be a vampire though.
I’m already a werewolf.
Wait, WHAT?
You’re a werewolf?!
Yeah, I was gonna tell you this when I woke up.
No time like the present though I suppose haha.
But yeah, I’ve been a werewolf my whole life.
Passed down from my mom.
I didn’t bite you last night, did I?
Not that I know of but that’s not what’s important right now!
Why didn’t you tell me this last night?
Hey, I could ask you the same thing!
True.
I mean, we were a bit rough with each other.
Yeah, now that I think about it, sort of makes sense now haha.
I thought you were gonna tell me you were a werewolf or something actually.
I didn’t even know they were real until now!
Yeah and apparently vampires are too haha.
Is this also a condition passed down from your great grandfather?
Passed down from my great-great-great-great grandfather actually.
Let me guess, Dracula haha?
Nah, just some guy named Vlad. He’s not famous or anything.
The whole image of vampirism though is so distorted after hundreds of years.
They get so much stuff wrong now in pop culture.
I know, right?! Same with werewolves.
You ever see An American Werewolf in London?
Yeah, that’s a great movie.
Totally full of shit. Turning into a werewolf isn’t nearly that scary.
As long as you know when it’s gonna be a full moon, it’s fine.
I’m a little bit taller, a lot more hairier for a few hours then I’m fine.
Really? That’s interesting. Same with vampires though.
I mean, we don’t live in coffins. We can still go outside when it’s sunny.
We’re just a little extra bloodthirsty and we can’t really go to church.
But I’m a Buddhist anyway so it doesn’t really affect me.
Hahaha really?
Yeah, it’s really popular among vampires. You have no idea.
I’m bet. But anyway, so, yeah, thanks for telling me about your “condition”.
I appreciate it.
But I’m not a vampire.
You sure?
Justin, I saw my reflection in the mirror as I was throwing up.
I’m pretty sure haha.
Hahaha okay good. I’m glad to hear that.
I’m usual pretty careful about this sort of thing.
Something about me just let that inner vampire within you come out?
You’re lucky it wasn’t a full moon last night haha.
That would have been interesting for sure.
Well, if you are a vampire, you would have been fine.
Werewolves don’t have wooden teeth haha.
Very true haha.
And vampires don’t have any silver bullets on them so you’d be fine.
I mean, I’m a pacifist anyway so I would never have a gun on me.
A pacifist, Buddhist vampire?
Next thing you’ll tell me you’re a vegan.
Oh no, I’m not that bad haha.
Good because...
it’d be hard to have dinner together tomorrow since I love steakhouses.
Wait, so, you still want to talk me? After all this?
Dude, honestly, how could we not haha?
That’s a very good point.
Wait, was that supposed to be a vampire pun?
Maybe…
Oh jeez haha.
